<bibRefCitation id="EFBA4B5CFFB9FF896F55FA2953DAF9F5" author="Bezdek, A." pageId="5" pageNumber="541" pagination="249 - 280" refId="ref6643" refString="Bezdek, A. (2016) Rhizotrogini. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Volume 3. Scarabaeoidea, Scirtoidea, Dascilloidea, Buprestoidea, Byrrhoidea. Revised and updated edition. Brill, Leiden, Boston, pp. 249 - 280." type="book chapter" year="2016">Bezděk (2016)</bibRefCitation>
